Repost from @birdsbinus

It's our pleasure to represent Binus University in Joint Statement Forum 2016 in Paramadina University from 20 - 22 September 2016.

Discussing innovative and brilliant solution to develop our National Defense Industry especially in Maritime sector, in order to face external threat whether it traditional or not. Also as the response of our government campaign about Global Maritime Fulcrum.

We realize this topic is classified topic in Indonesia, since the parties who ideally discuss about it are government and qualified scientist.

But, we feel the contribution of us as student of International Relations is needed in order to give another perspective for ther better future of Indonesia.

Our recommendation has been explained in front of Executive Officer of President in National Palace. We hope our ideas could help government to develop our maritime defense industry.

You can access our recommendations on

http://ksp.go.id/gagasan-pertahanan-nasional-dari-forum-mahasiswa/
